data.description: Welcome home to this 4 bed 2 bath rancher with a fully finished basement and fenced in backyard. Main floor living plus a 2 car garage and RV bay with no HOA situated on a large .33 lot on a dead end road with no current rear neighbors. The large yard has a shed and multiple fruit trees, chicken coop/run, where as the inside has tons of space and storage, beautiful fireplace focal points, a built in hutch and added sun room. Another unique feature about this home is the basement has access from inside the home and a private entrance from the garage, with the right creativity this home could serve as a multigenerational step up.
